e.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n阿伯都啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"594f6d19703c04c989a52505eaecda1b48b8de08","tid":114052,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T13:33:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做乜姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a0f213cc51cdd5f5ff4dbc6b65bbc78da9b7631","tid":114052,"uid":6431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T13:45:11.000Z","msg":"作出違反自然性交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n姐係色誘到佢黎仆就唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef11c43f212177f0203abc85db9778ee00e0521","tid":114052,"uid":44584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T13:46:44.000Z","msg":"CXXXXXXXX"},{"pid":"f886291907454ae91cddf7d4973e324f43f2ec15","tid":114052,"uid":44243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T13:46:54.000Z","msg":"女人比狗屌就睇到拍哂手<br />\n男人屌隻狗就咁多負評"},{"pid":"344e4ee905594454e648415c9de7336a5bf46dd9","tid":114052,"uid":80325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T13:49:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/